title: Garbage Warrior
description:
A documentary on the history of a building design called an "Earthship" and the legal battle by its inventor.

We all need to be aware of what we can do to stop the global warming disaster that is coming very rapidly.

yes I said it. GLOBAL WARMING. It is very real and, if not curbed NOW, will change the planet for the worse and our children's fate and their children's fate are uncertain if things don't start changing
